Surge Components Inc.


            
            Surge Components, Inc. engages in production and distribution of electronic products and components. Its products include capacitors; and discrete components, such as semiconductor rectifiers, transistors, and diodes. The company was founded on November 24, 1981 and is headquartered in Deer Park, NY.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


