Sponsored Topics








































See a problem?
Let us know!


  
  
            Surge Components is a competitive supplier of capacitors and discrete semiconductors with manufacturing facilities and sales offices located worldwide. The company is a progressive organization known for its product selection, service record and pricing. Surge s product offerings encompass aluminum electrolytic, film and multiple layer ceramic capacitors in standard market design, radial and axial packages. Surge s discrete products include bridge rectifiers, diodes and transient voltage suppressors. In addition, Surge is the North American marketing office for Lelon Electronics. Surge Components has offices in Deer Park, N.Y., and Kowloon, Hong Kong.
          






















